Package org.jgrapht.alg.vertexcover.util

Class RatioVertex<V>

java.lang.Object
org.jgrapht.alg.vertexcover.util.RatioVertex<V>
Type Parameters:
V - the graph vertex type
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<RatioVertex<V>>
public class RatioVertex<V> extends Object implements Comparable<RatioVertex<V>>
Helper class for vertex covers. Guarantees that vertices can be sorted, thereby obtaining a unique ordering.
Author:
Joris Kinable
